Burna Boy, together with his team and a few friends, celebrated his mother, Bose Ogulu, on her birthday by singing to her. As they sang, Burna proudly said, “I was the first” while his mother smiled at the love shown her. Below is a video of Burna Boy and his team serenading his mother. The post Burna boy and his team sings for his mother on her birthday (video) appeared first on YabaLeftOnline. Source: Yaba Left